g":"<blockquote>聽講細個有近視到大過就會冇<br />\n眼鏡反而加深度數</blockquote><br />\n一定唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細個有100度近視 冇戴眼鏡 <br />\n十幾年後而家多咗百幾度"},{"pid":"e8e0ee5678bc8636dda94dcf0172ce473efefec9","tid":233212,"uid":50176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T11:53:02.000Z","msg":"眼鏡其實有陰謀論"},{"pid":"c04a2bb6f1051eb0478ead5871da9fcb6d4681ee","tid":233212,"uid":55614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T11:54:00.000Z","msg":"無眼鏡咪做激光囉"},{"pid":"df67d4e024a4d5006bdebbc3708d6e5d7cb12d5e","tid":233212,"uid":5220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T11:55:38.000Z","msg":"聰明係古代原意係指耳聰目明<br />\n即係你視力聽力正常就算聰明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3604689b28965228ea8bc37f6143f65110e9558c","tid":233212,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T11:56:11.000Z","msg":"古代啲人要耕田同埋放牧，成日望好遠嘅嘢。所以，佢地視力不知幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b129009152ac4124782bc9425f8021e1931c8db","tid":233212,"uid":34793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T11:58:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>眼鏡其實有陰謀論</blockquote><br />\ndetail"},{"pid":"6370b60c2db9962d789b717b483b323705e40c6b","tid":233212,"uid":18265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T12:01:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聽講細個有近視到大過就會冇<br />\n眼鏡反而加深度數</blockquote><br />\n一定唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細個有100度近視 冇戴眼鏡 <br />\n十幾年後而家多咗百幾度</blockquote><br />\n細個百幾度 唔戴眼鏡 一年後二百幾 唔戴唔得"},{"pid":"b676af3f999ec231ee3b1117fb5d5192c9179f2a","tid":233212,"uid":36087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T12:12:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>古代啲人要耕田同埋放牧，成日望好遠嘅嘢。所以，佢地視力不知幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n反而係古時睇遠野會係一種才能<br />\n例如打仗既弓箭手<br />\n或者生活上打獵<br />\n都好睇對眼天生係咪高質<br />\n所以天生有近視既就少左呢方面出路<br />\n但一般都好難講咩叫有/冇近視<br />\n唔係視力極差既話，都係相對叫做正常視力姐"},{"pid":"3943dd753132285e26157b62da90315dce142bbc","tid":233212,"uid":41742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T12:15:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>行近D</blockquote><br />\n秒"},{"pid":"1d3ccb9d41ece7a70bb53da3bf12deca3c16c585","tid":233212,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T14:08:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>古代啲人要耕田同埋放牧，成日望好遠嘅嘢。所以，佢地視力不知幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n反而係古時睇遠野會係一種才能<br />\n例如打仗既弓箭手<br />\n或者生活上打獵<br />\n都好睇對眼天生係咪高質<br />\n所以天生有近視既就少左呢方面出路<br />\n但一般都好難講咩叫有/冇近視<br />\n唔係視力極差既話，都係相對叫做正常視力姐</blockquote><br />\n記得以前日本有個節目講世界上最厲害嘅人。有集講視力，都係蒙古草原生活同埋非洲大草原果啲人嘅視力最好。係好到有啲恐怖果隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1114991a3008512919b16c79196e668a67b4c5ad","tid":233212,"uid":59835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T14:14:20.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - tollis_peccata )"},{"pid":"e8ad3823a21840c96fea3aaf75ba4da34100f7a6","tid":233212,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T16:30:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20d53cfe7ce35a09758450e561793aac7a6f3d5c","tid":233212,"uid":32464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T18:03:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>古代啲人要耕田同埋放牧，成日望好遠嘅嘢。所以，佢地視力不知幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n反而係古時睇遠野會係一種才能<br />\n例如打仗既弓箭手<br />\n或者生活上打獵<br />\n都好睇對眼天生係咪高質<br />\n所以天生有近視既就少左呢方面出路<br />\n但一般都好難講咩叫有/冇近視<br />\n唔係視力極差既話，都係相對叫做正常視力姐</blockquote><br />\n記得以前日本有個節目講世界上最厲害嘅人。有集講視力，都係蒙古草原生活同埋非洲大草原果啲人嘅視力最好。係好到有啲恐怖果隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都記得有套講蒙古人 望超遠嘅字都望到<br />\n個陣諗係咪遠視 會唔會反而睇唔到近嘢"},{"pid":"165fe2c12c82d2f7e4cb5eb4e8e3f673ddeb3bee","tid":233212,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T18:10:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>古代啲人要耕田同埋放牧，成日望好遠嘅嘢。所以，佢地視力不知幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n反而係古時睇遠野會係一種才能<br />\n例如打仗既弓箭手<br />\n或者生活上打獵<br />\n都好睇對眼天生係咪高質<br />\n所以天生有近視既就少左呢方面出路<br />\n但一般都好難講咩叫有/冇近視<br />\n唔係視力極差既話，都係相對叫做正常視力姐</blockquote><br />\n記得以前日本有個節目講世界上最厲害嘅人。有集講視力，都係蒙古草原生活同埋非洲大草原果啲人嘅視力最好。係好到有啲恐怖果隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都記得有套講蒙古人 望超遠嘅字都望到<br />\n個陣諗係咪遠視 會唔會反而睇唔到近嘢</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=eASjoF8m9Xk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeASjoF8m9Xk&d=XkDMRo5st5VLQkVJYuplWPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=62736e84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=eASjoF8m9Xk</a>"},{"pid":"b613ab8fbd8500a24671052f1f983a9bd4629809","tid":233212,"uid":45821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T18:29:53.000Z","msg":"以前無咸片咪無打得打j  對眼咪唔會矇囉"}]}